# Dinaya stack

- Node.js 22, Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, Neon Postgres, Drizzle ORM, NextAuth, Vercel.
- Use the `@/` import alias.
- Domain logic lives in `src/lib/`; UI in `src/components/` and `src/app/`. Do not import components into lib.
- Match naming, types, and patterns in neighboring files; keep diffs minimal.

## Boundaries

- Never add `@cursor/sdk` or Cursor SDK dependencies to root `package.json` or `src/app/`.
- `.cursor/` and `AGENTS.md` are dev-only — not bundled for production.
- Product AI for tenants uses `src/lib/ai/` (Groq/OpenAI HTTP), not Cursor agents.

## Before finishing

Run `npm run verify` (lint + test + build) for any non-trivial change.
